videos.description: Josh Okogie gets the outlet pass and finishes with the easy two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Okogie opens up the scoring

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Jose Alvarado makes the 3-pointer with a little extra help from the rim.
videos.headline: Alvarado gets the friendly bounce

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Abdoulaye Gueye gets the block, Jose Alvarado takes it downcourt and finds Tadric Jackson for the layup.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech turns defense into offense

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Josh Okogie banks in the 3-pointer as the Yellow Jackets lead over Syracuse.
videos.headline: The bank is open for Okogie

videos.description: Syracuse's Oshae Brissett gets the steal and gets his head to the rim for the dunk.
videos.headline: Brissett's steal leads to huge dunk

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Josh Okogie takes advantage of the Syracuse mistake, takes the ball downcourt and finishes with the dunk. He then adds insult to injury by swinging on the rim.
videos.headline: Okogie slams it down
